The '''Condyle of humerus''' is the distal end of the [[humerus]]. It is made up of the [[Capitulum of humerus|capitulum]] and the [[Trochlea of humerus|trochlea]].<ref>xiphoid.biostr.washington.edu/fma/fmabrowser-hierarchy.html?search=Condyle of humerus</ref>

