'''''Debrecen Heliophysical Observatory''''' is an [[astronomy|astronomical]] [[observatory]] owned and operated by Konkoly Thege Miklós Astronomical Institute of [[Hungarian Academy of Sciences]]. The Observatory provides solar data and images of observation. Study solar flares and sunspots.<ref name=dezso> {{cite journal |last1=Dezső |first1=L. |year=1982 |title=Debrecen heliophysical observatory |journal=[[Solar Physics (journal)|Solar Physics]] |volume=79 |issue=1 |pages=195-199 |bibcode=1982SoPh...79..195D |doi=10.1007/BF00146983 }}</ref><ref name=67dezso> {{cite journal |last1=Dezső |first1=L. |year=1967 |title=Debrecen heliophysical observatory |journal=[[Solar Physics (journal)|Solar Physics]] |volume=2 |issue=1 |pages=129-130 |bibcode = 1967SoPh....2..129D |doi=10.1007/BF00155899 }}</ref>
